			<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Press Select at the music selection screen</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Secret (Play as Yumi) -
			<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Replace the game disc with the audio CD containing: ''The Twister'' after the game begins.</font><br>
